# -*-perl-*-

=head1 NAME

TEST1 - Basic Quick Look recipe for testing purposes

=head1 DESCRIPTION

Basic processing recipe suitable for DREAM/STARE images.

=head1 KNOWN ISSUES

This recipe can not handle time series observing modes.

